    "title": "Marketplace Manager - Dove India South Asia Partners - Freshers Welcome",
    "description": "Grow your career with Dove India South Asia Partners! We are hiring a Marketplace Manager for our Pune team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Dove India South Asia Partners:\nDove India South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Flexible working hours\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pune, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Dove India South Asia Partners!",
